  "instructions": [
    "Melt butter in a pot over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and red bell pepper and cook until softened.",
    "Stir in the mixed spice blend and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add flour to coat vegetables and cook for 1 minute, whisking constantly.",
    "Gradually pour in vegetable broth while whisking to create a smooth sauce.",
    "Add heavy cream, salt, and pepper, then bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Stir in shredded cheeses until melted and the soup is glossy.",
    "Serve hot, letting the creamy, spicy flavor soothe any hangover."
